{"type": "article", "id": 22057, "title": "Alphabear：用熊宝宝拼字，也不容易", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 998, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">Alphabear（<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/alphabear-word-puzzle-game/id930003798?ls=1&amp;mt=8\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">iPhone </a>|<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.spryfox.alphabear&amp;hl=en\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Android</a>）是 Spry Fox 开发的一款英文单词解谜游戏，主角是一头两头身的小熊，玩家拼出的单词越多，熊宝宝就长得越大。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606001756xusv4K6TRczIFw0b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87833828\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">另外，每局通关之后都能收集到不同造型的小熊，就像这样：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606060017576pblc2aKFYBeVRug.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.525\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606060017577lwPWzZcysH6faAb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.37272727\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n\n\n"}